Margaret Tallichet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Tallichet 0 Margaret "Talli" Tallichet (March 13, 1914 – May 3, 1991) was an actress and longtime wife of movie director William Wyler. Her best-known leading role was with Peter Lorre in the film noir Stranger on the Third Floor (1940).
